    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">Is your child a budding rock star? The Kidplokio Rockin’ Star karaoke machine is a great gift idea for your little one! It comes with everything a kid needs to put on their own musical performance - a real working karaoke microphone with a mic stand and realistic sound effect buttons. In addition to the above features, this fantastic karaoke machine comes with an MP3 connection so you can plug your MP3 in and play your child’s favorite songs so they can sing along! Singing and dancing is also a great way for children to practice their creativity, and imagination and get some fun indoor exercise. Our unique pretend play musical toy comes with an automatic shutdown mode - the karaoke machine will turn off by itself after 5 minutes of no use to conserve energy</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">Kidplokio Musical Microphone Pretend Play Karaoke Machine Kids MP3 Player</h2>\n  <p>Is your child a budding rock star? The Kidplokio Rockin’ Star karaoke machine is a great gift idea for your little one! It comes with everything a kid needs to put on their own musical performance - a real working karaoke microphone with a mic stand and realistic sound effect buttons.</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li>KID’S KARAOKE FUN - Kidplokio Rockin’ Star karaoke machine comes with everything a kid needs to put on their very own musical performance; a real working microphone with a mic stand that has realistic sound effects</li>\n    <li>MP3 CONNECTION - Connect your MP3 player to the sing along karaoke machine so your child can play their favorite songs and practice their rock star skills; encourages creativity and imagination</li>\n    <li>SHUTDOWN MODE - Karaoke machine automatically shuts down after 5 minutes with no use (except for MP3 mode) to conserve energy; Requires (3) AA batteries, not included</li>\n    <li>DURABLE AND KID-SAFE - Made of high-quality, durable plastic that can be wiped clean and dried as needed; Safe for children ages 3 and up with parental supervision</li>\n    <li><strong>SPECIFICATIONS - Colors:</strong> blue, white, yellow; Sound effect buttons: yes; Material: plastic: Batteries required: (3) AA, not included; Shutdown mode: yes; Recommended age: 3 years and up</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/1000x1000/toys/AQ1515_karaoke_machine_BLU_packaging_03.jpg\" alt=\"Is your child a budding rock star\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> KPKARKBLU1</li>\n    <li><strong>UPC:</strong> 810058448255</li>\n    <li><strong>Size:</strong> Large</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>In addition to the above features, this fantastic karaoke machine comes with an MP3 connection so you can plug your MP3 in and play your child’s favorite songs so they can sing along! Singing and dancing is also a great way for children to practice their creativity, and imagination and get some fun indoor exercise.</p>\n  <p>Our unique pretend play musical toy comes with an automatic shutdown mode - the karaoke machine will turn off by itself after 5 minutes of no use to conserve energy. The machine requires (3) AA batteries (not included).</p>\n  <p>Made of high-quality, durable plastic, this machine can easily be wiped down and dried off as needed to keep it clean in between uses. It comes with a cardboard box so you can pack it up to store for later use. These machines are safe for children ages 3 and up with adult supervision, so grab one of these for your little one and watch them star in their own shows!</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
